<title>ạnt ạlly ḥbytny</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 ạ- ạnt ạlly ḥbytny wbdmk fạdytny ʿlsẖạn tkẖlṣny mwt ʿly ạlṣlyb

[V2]
 ḥrrt kyạny wnzʿt ạḥzạny kẖlạṣk mjạny yạ ạʿẓm ṭbyb

[V3]
 ạlqrạr - ( sẖkrạaⁿ sydy kẖlytny frḥạn .. wbdmk ạdytny llạbdyẗ ḍmạn ) 2

[V4]
 2- ạnt ṣạḥb ạlqwẗ ksrt qyd ạlḥyẗ wḥyạty ạljạyẗ mlkk yạ yswʿ

[V5]
 ʿmry hạʿysẖẗ lyk ḥyạty mlk lyk dạymạaⁿ hạ ạʿlyk qdạm ạljmwʿ

[V6]
 3- yạlly ạdytny ḥyạẗ wqdmt ạlfdạʾ wkmạn fy ạlsmạʾ ạʿddt ly mkạn

[V7]
 bʿd mạ knt ʿạṣy wmyt fy ạlmʿạṣy bqyt ạnt kẖlạṣy yạ ạlhy ạlḥnạn

[V8]
 4- fy ạymạnk tẖbtny bklạmk ạsndny bwʿwdk ʿyny fy ạlmsẖwạr mʿạk

[V9]
 ʿạysẖ sạjd lyk kl rjạyạ fyk wạnạ ʿnd qdmyk wlgẖạyẗ mạ ạlqạk</lyrics>
